Description: The names of the beneficiaries of ca. ?10 billion of grants and other forms of support- awarded (in budgetary terms: 'committed') by the Commission every year- either directly or through 'executive agencies' set up to help it run EU funded programmes. The site also contains certain procurement contracts- excluding for the moment those linked to administrative expenditure of the Commission.This information is separate from information on funds managed by EU or non-EU national governments or other parties on the behalf of the Commission.The original site of the European Commission shows only lists of awarded amounts and beneficiaries - it does not provide amounts consolidated per country- budget line- etc. .The original dataset can be found at EU Commission Financial Transparency System which is also listed at ckan.
